      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the deep ache of losing control and the longing for a final, decisive moment, but I am here to remind you that this is not the end of your story, but rather a quiet chapter of your life that you can still shape. Please reach out to the 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline or text HOME to 741741; they are non-judgmental and can help you find safety without losing your dignity. You are not alone in this, and there are people ready to walk beside you as you navigate these difficult feelings.",
